        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Made of materials scavenged from wild places, a <em>druid's crown</em> can be rebuilt for a variety of benefits. The crown grants you a +1 item bonus to a skill and can be activated to cast a spell, both depending on the material used to build the crown, as listed on the table below. If you invest and wear <em>living mantle</em> along with the crown, the crown's item bonus increases by 1 and its spell's DC rises to 27.</p>\n<p>You can invest this item only if you're a druid. When you do, as a 10-minute activity that has the manipulate trait, you can disassemble and rebuild the crown with different materials, changing its item bonus and spell accordingly.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The crown casts its spell at 2nd level (DC 20).</p><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You are a druid.</p><table class=\"pf2e\"><thead><tr><th>Material</th><th>Item Bonus</th><th>Spell</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"height:51px\"><td style=\"height:51px\">Antlers</td><td style=\"height:51px\">Intimidation</td><td style=\"height:51px\">@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enlarge]</td></tr><tr style=\"height:51px\"><td style=\"height:51px\">Flowers</td><td style=\"height:51px\">Diplomacy</td><td style=\"height:51px\">@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Animal Allies]</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\">Leaves</td><td style=\"height:17px\">Stealth</td><td style=\"height:17px\">@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.One with Plants]</td></tr></tbody></table>"
